response.Q0: To use the inspector as quickly as possible to get a good range of where the highest positive numbers were located. This increased my chances of getting more money
response.Q1: Yes, By thinking faster and avoiding making mistakes such as not selecting the right path for the spider to move. Also memorising the highest positive numbers I saw from the inspectors in order to decide which route is best.
response.Q2: It was a bit challenging as I just had to get used to the rules and not forget about using the inspector as fast as possible. If I took more than two seconds to use it when starting the round then I would have to play the round blind without knowing which path to take.
